    <h1>About SSRSD</h1>
    <p>SSRSD (Semantic Search and Recommendation in Series Data) is a web platform meant to help you find your TV series with ease. Not only does it do that, it also suggests new series for you to watch, based on your searches.</p>
    <p>SSRSD can be used either with simple keywords ('action', 'Modern Family', 'Benedict Cumberbatch') or with more complex sentences, like 'Action series by BBC with Benedict Cumberbatch'.</p>
